high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right of the bed to exit the room and face the grey sofa on the right.
Pick up the knife from the couch.
Cut the potato in the pan with the knife.
Put the knife back on the sofa.
Pick up a slice of the potato from the pan on the couch.
Turn around and walk left to enter the dining room to reach the microwave on the left.
Heat the slice of potato in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and walk left to exit the room and walk to the bedroom on the left to reach the sidetable next to the bed.
Put the slice of potato on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the heated slice of Potato on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sofa.
Take the knife from the couch.
There is a potato on the couch.
Cut the potato into pieces on the sofa with the knife.
Placed the knife on the couch and take the piece of potato.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the potato into the oven and baked.
Take it out from the oven and go to the sidetable.
Put the potato on the sidetable of the bedroom.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato on the SideTable of the bedroom.

high_descs: Walk outside the room through an exit in the opposite corner, and go right across the hall until you reach the right side of the sofa.
Pick up the knife from the sofa.
Using the knife, slice a potato that lies on a plate on the sofa.
Put the knife back where you took it from the sofa.
Pick up a potato slice from the plate.
Turn around and as you walk straight up, head to the first entrance you see on your left, then walk to the room's opposite side where you approach the microwave.
Put the potato slice in the microwave, heat it up for a while, then take the potato out from the microwave.
Leave the room you are in, then immediately go inside a room adjacent to the left of the room you were in, where you head to the opposite corner with a sidetable.
Put the potato on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place the heated-up potato on the SideTable.
